Bulklegs AS3
http://github.com/percentjuice/bulkylegs
built 17.01.2010
updated 16.04.2010
updated 01.10.2010
merges the Robotlegs AS3 Micro-Architecture with BulkLoader's asset loading tools and XML parsing.

INSTALLATION
This is an AS3 library, a compiled swc is included.  It is built to be referenced independently, as a module.  See LIBARARIES below for referenced libraries.  Run test/BulkyLegsTestSuite.as to assess basic operation.

LIBRARIES
Robotlegs AS3 Micro-Architecture 
http://www.robotlegs.org
Bulk-Loader
http://code.google.com/p/bulk-loader/
AS3 CORE-LIB
https://github.com/mikechambers/as3corelib

USAGE
The bulkyLegs wiki is the best place to get started:
http://wiki.github.com/percentjuice/bulkylegs/

